"freelancers and small organizations. It is built to cater to both corporate "
"clients (team building events, professional events, product photography) and "
"individual\n"
"            clients (weddings, family events, pregnancy shoots, pet shoots, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Denne branche er udviklet til små fotostudier, freelancere og mindre "
"organisationer. Den er beregnet til både erhvervskunder (teambuilding-"
"arrangementer, firmaevents og produktfotografering) og privatkunder\n"
"            (bryllupper, familiefester, graviditetsfotografering, "
"kæledyrsbilleder osv.)."

